name_for_human: Generate Image Condition On Pose Image
description_for_human: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and a human pose image.
description_for_model: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and a human pose image. like: generate a real image of a human from this human pose image, or generate a new real image of a human from this pose. The input to this tool should be the image_path and the user description
